Whoa, there!  I'm with you on the evils of civil asset forfeiture and other
abuses, but you're engaging in collectivist thinking if you claim that law
enforcement deserves no respect whatsoever.  This is unreasonable.  Just
because there are some bad apples - okay, many - doesn't mean they're all bad.


